://www.nme.com/artists/megadeth">Megadeth</a>名列前茅。</p><p>摇滚和金属音乐节将于 2024 年 6 月 27 日至 30 日在法国克利松举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-offspring">The Offspring</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dropkick-murphys">Dropkick Murphys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babymetal">Babymetal</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nova-twins">Nova Twins</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-interrupters">The Interrupters</a>等众多乐队都将在此演出。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-garbage-and-the-offspring-kroq-almost-acoustic-christmas-2023-line-up-3520605">Red Hot Chili Peppers、Garbage 和 The Offspring 领军的 KROQ 几乎 Acoustic 2023 年圣诞节阵容</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
